name: Ashlee Graham - Smoking #1
description:
This is Ashlee Graham in my garage in 2009. I'm pretty sure this was well before she ever started doing porn but I can't be 100% on that. She was a real sweetheart, if a little bratty and glued to her phone that first shoot:) I shot her again a couple of years ago and she's still just as sweet. I'll probably wind up saying that about a lot of the models I've shot, but then if they weren't nice you probably wouldn't be seeing photos of them. Ain't nobody got time for bullshit;)

This is my 8th NFT. I've decided my initial offering this first two days in the NFT space will be 10 pieces that show the general feel of my work. After that I'm going to think on it a bit and probably limit my minting to a small weekly drop. As this is literally only my second day in the space, that is subject to change of course but I thought I would give at least somewhat of a roadmap of my plans. 

Thank you to everyone who has shown me love so far. I really appreciate it and I can't wait to see where this goes.
